						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone (No. 10) set up in a field to the west of the village.</p>						

						<p>Circa 10th century.</p>						

						<p>This registers the death of Sattiyapaḷi (?) grandson of Chaṭṭagamuṇḍa in a skirmish when Pallavaraya, bearing the epithet <hi rend="italic">gaṇḍaroḷgaṇḍa,</hi> captured the cattle of Maṅgala.</p>						

						</summary>
